title: Big.Brother.Australia.AU.Series.2
description:
Although this is just one disc it is the complete Big Brother Australia series 2. It is in WMV format and has very small file sizes. The quality is just okay but like the celebrity version this is the only copy I know of.  

I will put up series 1 in a few days and it is in AVI format and is 4 discs. Keep in mind these early series were not capped and encoded in great quality so even series 1 doesn't have great quality. 

If you like BBAU then I'm sure you'll have no problem with the quality if you really want to see them. Enjoy and please help seed.
